d new light on the\nrelationship between scale and generalization.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Oct 2021 19:07:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 18 Oct 2021 18:55:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-20"}
