ibility of the local pseudogenerator as a viable tool for enforcing gauge\ninvariance in modern quantum simulators and NISQ devices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Oct 2021 18:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-18"}
